Breakable Pillars (Using Fake 'DMM')

Made by The Giblets of Jesus

___________________________________ Like my old Pillar Prefab, these new pillars feature the same basic structure for destruction, but are now cheaper to render, Gib more realistically and overall, work a lot better. The Pillars are constructed from lots of small func_physboxes (Already fully optimized) that begin to move once damaged, creating for a very relistic looking effect that has the potential to really spice up a dull map and even increase the size of your penis! Well, maybe... As always, if you do choose to use this prefab in one of your fine submissions, I'll ask you put me in the credits :). ___________________________________
